CONVERSATION TITLE: Emerging trends in B2B sales
CONTENT:
Dear Kalash,


Over the past few months, COVID-19 has definitively changed the way we interact with our customers.


We surveyed more than 1,000 buyers and sellers in India to uncover both emerging and enduring trends for LinkedIn’s annual State of Sales report. One of the most telling findings is that leading through change is now the critically required skill for sales leaders. Some of the other interesting data points from this year’s survey were:


  • Customer satisfaction is now the #1 measure of sales performance
  • Sales intelligence tools have become “extremely critical” in closing deals for 74% of sales professionals leveraging technology to sell
  • The data-driven organisation is on the rise with data being used for everything from prospecting accounts to evaluating closed-won business.

In this environment, I hope the State of Sales 2020: India Edition will give you valuable insight to help you, and your team, navigate these changes and be better partners to your customers.


Best,


Grace Kerrison

LinkedIn Sales Solutions
